'ai-workflow-automator','AI Workflow Automator','Replace manual business processes with AI agents that run 24/7','Map a manual workflow, build a webhook trigger, implement each step as an AI agent function, and chain them with structured error handling and Slack notifications.','ai-llm',NULL,
